# Documentation — single source of truth

- **README.md** contains the full project structure, architecture, flows, API map, and troubleshooting.
- Never recreate `DOCUMENTACAO_COMPLETA.md` or duplicate architecture docs elsewhere.
- When changing architecture, controllers, API endpoints, settings schema, or startup flow → update **README.md** in the same session/PR.
- Technical backlog (bugs, improvements, audit findings) goes in **AI_GUIDELINES.md**, not in README section 22.9 long lists.
- Historical forensic report stays in `relatorio_auditoria_bot.md`; new findings get an entry in `AI_GUIDELINES.md`.
